    "Disposition": {
      "text": "Discharge with ophtho follow-up (if no improvement) in 3 - 4 days\nBacterial conjunctivitis is highly contagious. Patients may return to work or school after 24 hours of topical therapy and a reduction in discharge from eye(s). Advise good hygiene practices.",
